          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Deuterated polyethylene targets CD(2) of about",
                " 190 ug/cm2 was bombarded a 22 MeV Be-9 beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A silicon delta-E-E telescope was placed at",
                " about 70 cm from the target with an angle of about",
                " 45-degree for a continuous monitoring of the target",
                " thickness during the experiment.",
                "The particle detection was performed by using two",
                " silicon delta-E-E telescopes with a position-sensitive",
                " detector (PSD) as E.",
                "Energy calibration was performed by means of a standard",
                " three-peak alpha source and alpha and Li-6 particles",
                " from C-12(Li-6,a)N-14 and C-12(Li-6,Li-6)C-12",
                " reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TROJA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Reaction H-2(Be-9,a+Li-6)n was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "THEO"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By author*.The results of the study of the two-body",
                " Be-9(p,a)Li-6 reaction, obtained through the",
                " application of the trojan-horse-method to the three-",
                " body H-2(Be-9,a+Li-6)n reaction were presented."
              ]
            }
          ],
